---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About" description="About EtherFun Lab" lang="en">
  <article class="prose dark:prose-invert max-w-content mx-auto">
    <h1>About</h1>
    <p>
      <strong>EtherFun Lab</strong> is the engineering &amp; product blog of the
      EtherFun team. We share what we learn while building — design tradeoffs,
      engineering practice, and observations on the industries we work in.
    </p>
    <h2>Topics</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="/tags/eros-engine/">#eros-engine</a> — our open-source AI companion engine</li>
      <li><a href="/tags/memory/">#memory</a> — long-term memory architectures for AI agents</li>
      <li><a href="/tags/rust/">#rust</a> — engineering practice in Rust</li>
      <li><a href="/tags/pgvector/">#pgvector</a> — vector search inside Postgres</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>Stay in touch</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>RSS: <a href="/rss.xml">/rss.xml</a></li>
      <li>GitHub: <a href="https://github.com/etherfunlab" rel="noopener">github.com/etherfunlab</a></li>
    </ul>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
